<div type="definition">
<p>HOT LIGHT which APPEARS ABOVE what BURNS.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for fire is huǒ 火.</p>
<p>2. Yán 炎 refers specifically to the flame.</p></div>
